SPIFFE ID:
spiffe://bank.com/prod/digital-agent-proxy
The Digital Agent has a policy like:
Only these services may call me:
✔ spiffe://bank.com/prod/digital-agent-proxy
✔ spiffe://bank.com/prod/orchestrator

❌ spiffe://bank.com/prod/policy-agent
